ABC Capital Selects International Business Machines Corp's IBM PureSystems over Oracle, Dell and HP
Thursday, 31 Oct 2013 10:00am EDT
International Business Machines Corp announced that ABC Capital, has deployed a solution based on PureSystems technology. The new solution will help the Company simplify and integrate their existing platforms allowing them to provide new products and offers for consumers. After considering other vendors including HP, Dell and Oracle, ABC Capital chose to consolidate its entire IT infrastructure onto IBM PureSystems.Â 
